org.nbena.beersmanager.sclasses

Class BeerJSONSaveSpecialClass

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nbena.beersmanager.sclasses.BeerJSONSaveSpecialClass

  • public class BeerJSONSaveSpecialClass
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a modified version of #org.nbena.beersmanager.coreclasses.Beer(), made to be saved into the beer file. To save space, I modify the style and the brewery property of the "normal class" and replaced them by a normal string. It means that when you read the beers, you need to re-create the normal class by linking each beer to its brewery and its style basing on their name.
    Author:
    nbena
    See Also:
    Beer
